      "topic": "颗粒流",
      "title": "测试节点",
      "type": "FORMULA",
      "latex": "$$\\text{test} \\ \\int \\hat{\\vec{\\mathcal{L}}^{2^{2_2a}}_\\pi} \\ \\frac{\\mathrm{d}}{\\mathrm{d}y} \\ \\ \\Delta \\ \\Delta x (\\alpha_1) \\epsilon' e^{-E/kT} e_1 \\partial t$$\n\n$$\\mathcal{Z}_{eff}^{(n)}[\\phi] = \\oint_{\\partial \\Omega} \\sqrt{-g} \\cdot e^{-\\frac{i}{\\hbar} \\int_{t_0}^{t_1} \\left[ \\frac{1}{2} m \\left( \\frac{\\mathrm{d}^2 \\vec{x}_a}{\\mathrm{d}s^2} \\right)^2 - V(x_a, \\dot{x}_a, \\vec{p}^{(i)}) \\right] \\mathrm{d}s} \\cdot \\frac{\\delta^2 S}{\\delta \\phi^* \\delta \\phi}$$\n\n$$\\mathbb{W}_{ext} = \\int \\mathrm{d}^4x \\left\\{ \\bar{\\psi}_{\\alpha} (i \\gamma^{\\mu} \\nabla_{\\mu} - m) \\psi^{\\alpha} + \\sum_{j=1}^{N} \\det \\left( \\begin{matrix} \\hat{A}_{ij} & \\delta_{ij} \\Phi \\\\ \\Phi^{\\dagger} & \\partial^2 \\hat{B}_{ij} \\end{matrix} \\right) \\right\\} + \\Delta \\mathcal{L}_{int}$$\n\n## 1\n\n$$\\chi_{i j}^{(3)}(\\omega_p; \\omega_1, \\omega_2) = \\frac{N e^4}{\\epsilon_0 \\hbar^3} \\sum_{a,b,c} \\frac{\\rho_{aa}^{(0)} - \\rho_{bb}^{(0)}}{(\\omega_{ba} - \\omega_1 - i\\Gamma_{ba}) (\\omega_{ca} - \\omega_p - i\\Gamma_{ca})} \\hat{r}_{ab} \\hat{r}_{bc} \\hat{r}_{ca}$$",
      "desc": "",
      "references": "",
